# AssetProof — local environment configuration
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# .env.local is never committed to source control.

# ── Proof publishing ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# PROOF_PUBLISHER_NETWORK controls which publish path is used.
# Omit or leave blank to use dry-run mode (no chain config required).
#
# Supported values:
#   bas-direct   — Off-chain BAS attestation via EAS SDK (preferred).
#                  Requires BAS_SCHEMA_UID + BAS_PRIVATE_KEY below.
#                  No gas or RPC call needed. Produces a signed EIP-712 attestation.
#   relay        — POST the proof payload to PROOF_PUBLISHER_ENDPOINT.
#                  The relay handles chain submission (BSC testnet or mainnet).
#   bsc-testnet  — Legacy alias for relay, accepted for backward compatibility.
#
# PROOF_PUBLISHER_NETWORK=bas-direct
# PROOF_PUBLISHER_NETWORK=relay
# PROOF_PUBLISHER_ENDPOINT=https://your-relay.example.com/attest
# PROOF_PUBLISHER_API_KEY=

# ── BAS direct (off-chain attestation via EAS SDK) ───────────────────────────
#
# Required for bas-direct mode:
#
#   BAS_SCHEMA_UID
#     bytes32 UID of a schema registered on the BAS Schema Registry.
#     Register the schema string from src/lib/proof/bas.ts using the
#     BAS Schema Registry contract at BAS_CONTRACT_ADDRESS.
#     Example: 0xabcdef...64hexchars
#
#   BAS_PRIVATE_KEY
#     Hex-encoded 32-byte private key used to sign attestations.
#     The corresponding address is embedded in each attestation (signerAddress).
#     Use a dedicated key — not a wallet holding funds.
#     0x-prefix is optional.
#
# Optional:
#
#   BAS_CHAIN_ID
#     Chain ID for EIP-712 domain (default: 97, BSC testnet).
#     Use 56 for BSC mainnet.
#
#   BAS_CONTRACT_ADDRESS
#     BAS/EAS contract address for EIP-712 domain binding.
#     Default: 0x6c2270298b1e6046898a322acBC5b1f9b4d16e80 (BSC / BSC testnet).
#     Required if you deploy BAS to a custom address.
#
# BAS_SCHEMA_UID=0x...
# BAS_PRIVATE_KEY=0x...
# BAS_CHAIN_ID=97
# BAS_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x6c2270298b1e6046898a322acBC5b1f9b4d16e80
